===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|衣|集|c1=s|c2=p|ls=psc}} with an original reference to a combination of various colours put together, perhaps linked to dyed clothes. A more comprehensible variant is [[襍]].

===Etymology===
Cognate with {{och-l|集|to gather; to collect}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}). Note similarities to {{cog|my|သုပ်|t=to mix ingredients}}.

